Subject: top 10 signs yer VW needs recall

10 steering wheel is in the back seat.

09 you're constantly stopping for coffe to keep from 
   dozing off from the carbon monoxide.

08 mix up at factory gave you anti-lock radio and 
   am/fm brakes

07 the roof rolls back, but it's not a convertible.

06 if you're in an accident, you have to call a guy to 
   inflate your airbags

05 hazard light on dash reminds you to sign will

04 horn emits very soft meow

03 warning on tires reads: "FOR INDOOR USE ONLY"

02 0-60 in seven weeks

01 any part of the car may be used as a cigarette lighter

